Tebṛeq, terɛeḍ, nesla i tuɣac, tezlez lqaɛa, seg wasmi i d-țwaxelqen ṭṭlam ɣef tmurt meṛṛa ; lameɛna armi ur d-yeǧǧi acemma, neɣ m'ulac laẓ-nni.
