Lameɛna kra lɛulama n ccariɛa țqelliben kan ɣef lǧil n Sidna Ɛisa, yewweḍ-ed lweqt anda ara t-yeṭṭef wasif. Ad ițțusemmi daɣen temdinin n ?ur imeqqranen akk-d Sidun. Mcbuṭin-nni, ad sburren ticekkaṛin n tegzirt n Kritus deg ulli n Yiriku, anda i gețțuṣun lexṣaṣ.
Yessetma-s seddaw leḥkum n umenɣi ɣef tmura n Ṛuman.
Yefka lameṛ i yiwen n lfesyan ad iɛass Sidna Ɛisa a ten-yeǧǧ ad yezzenz. Yefka lameṛ i wid yessnen ad ɛummen, ad ḍeggṛen iman-nsen d imezwura ɣer waman iwakken ad awḍen ɣer rrif n temdint n Ṛuma.
Imezdaɣ n temdint n Atinya akk-d ibeṛṛaniyen i gzedɣen dinna, ḥemmlen ad sɛeddin lweqt-nsen anagar deg usigna.
Ayagi yedṛa-d iwakken ad yețțusellek wid i gḍaɛen di leqsed nsen. Llan daɣen wid i d-yegran neɣ wid iwumi țwakksen iqeṛṛay ɣef ddemma n idammen.
Imezdaɣ n tmurt uggaden, dɣa iweḥḥa-yas-ed Sidi Ṛebbi, yesnejmaɛ-ed deg waṭas yid-sen, daymi ur nezmir ara a d-nekcef ayen i gxulfen tikli di liman.
Leɛqiṛa tețwaṭṭef nețțat d lemtel kan n wayen yellan deg-nneɣ. Leɛqiṛa-agi i gețwaxedmen s yiwet n tikkelt kan, meɛna ur tebɛid ara, ur țfeṛṛiḥ ara am tjeḥnaṛt-nni lɣella n mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb,
Sidna Ɛisa iweṣṣa-ten, yenna-yas : ?ṭfet-eț sin wussan i deg ara teswem ssuq mbla ma nesɛa ayen ara ḥwiǧen.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) akk-d laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d yir lecɣal-nsen.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen yelhan, ilaq ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ;
Ini-yi-d yiwen n leswaṛ n temdint n Zabadi, wis tlata s wezṛu yellan di tmurt-nni, yeɛni qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer tmezduɣt-nni.
Argaz-agi ixeddem akka imi d ameksa kan yețwaxelṣen, mačči d wid i t-islemden.
Yerna m'ara d-yaweḍ wayen innekmalen, ad slen i wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen, ad qedcen di tejmaɛt n watmaten yellan di temdint n Lquds iwakken ad qqimen d win ixeddmen ayen akken i wen-d-ihegga, ad ilin d sebba n tuccḍa akk-d lmeṣbeḥ, wid i gxeddmen yis-sen s tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi.
A d-yas lweqt i deg ara yedṛu wayen yuran di tektabt n ?abur : Iwakken aț-țețmeslayeḍ, aț-țnegreḍ, aț-țnehhuḍ, aț-țnehhuḍ, aț-țețweṣṣiḍ tis snat.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem,
Ini i yemɣaṛen ad setqenɛen, ad fken leqdeṛ i yiman-nsen, ad sɛun leɛqel, ad amnen s tlata iberdan, ad fehmen akken ilaq.
Ur neǧhid ara di liman, ur țțaǧat ara iman-nsent ɣef wayen ara neslemden, țemcabin ɣer webrid wayen yesɛan azal n tlata umitrat, seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit ;
Ma d wid yettabaɛen cci n ddunit ɣellin deg ujeṛṛeb akk-d tfextin n yir ccehwat n tnefsit-nsen, i gețțawin deg-nsen ɣer txeṣṣart akk-d nnger. Ma yella daɣen kra n win ixeddmen cceṛ, ur zmiren ara ad țwajeṛben, ggaren iman-nsen d lbeṛhanat i xeddmen am wigi.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, axaṭer ččuṛen d zzux i d-yekkan s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi s lḥeṛma, d leqheṛ i gețṛaǧu deg-sen a ten-rebḥen mbla tugdi.
ilaq ad yili win ara d-yesfehmen, ad ssusmen axiṛ di ddunit, axaṭer ur zmiren ara ad fehmen ayen akk i d-ssufuɣen seg webrid neɣ ad ilin di mkul amkan.
Imi tessazdgem tamusni d ayen i tesɛan ɣer tmusni, ilaq ad tnerni s tezmert n wawal-nni ;
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut liman am tseddarit s wayes ara tizmirem aț-țsensem isufa n tmes n Cciṭan ;
Yerna m'ur sɛint ara ayen ara xedment, ad țcalint seg wexxam ɣer wayeḍ mačči neɣ imi ur sɛin ara ccɣel, meɛna ad kettṛent deg ufus-nsent.
A d-ilul afus-is ɣer weqṛaḥ n tarrawt rriḥa, melmi ara yessers ufus-is di lqaɛa ?
ifassen n yemdanen țwaxedṣen s ufus-is i gella yid-sen.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen azal n telmeẓyan akk-d meyya iseggasen.
Kra iɛeqqayen nniḍen ɣlin deg waṭas n tudrin m'ara slen i wawal, m'ara d-immektin Lmasiḥ, ad țrun aṭas ;
Asm'ara tels lǧețța-agi irekkun ayen ur nrekku, asmi ara tels lǧețța-agi ara yemten ayen ur nețmețțat, ad yedṛu wannect-a.
Imi temmuzeɣleḍ ur teḥmiḍ, tsemmḍeḍ, teḥliḍ akk-d yiḍ deg uzniḍ-ik, iwɛeṛ fell-ak aț-țeẓẓuḍ.
A k-n-ssutreɣ ɣef wunyir-iw akken ilaq, ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa akk-d mitin neɣ tlata iberdan.
Yessetma-s aț-țerrem taktabt-nni tettebɛeḍ, teṭṭfeḍ aṣurdi n wass !
Ur iḥunn ara ayen yedṛan di tmurt n Selyan yellan di tmurt n Asya. Mi qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, yusa-d ɣer temdint n Biri. Di lweqt-nni, qṛib a d-kkren wat Isṛail ger temdinin n Libya.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yesselmaden lekdeb i gḥekkmen ɣef lɛeskeṛ n Ṛuman tamdint n Stuwis, tamdint n Lud.
Yewweḍ-ed wass n Tfaska n weɣṛum mbla iɣes n tamtunt i deg ilaq ad zlun Marṭa, yeɛni « Bunṭuḥ n temdint n Filibus », yeɛni ass n tuɣalin n Ssid-nneɣ Ɛisa Lmasiḥ.
Meɛna aṭas seg wid i gɣilen ad ḥețțmen fell-awen ṭṭhaṛa, bɣan a d-sbeggnen iman-nsen zdat inelmaden.
Argaz-agi ixeddem akka imi d ameksa kan yețwaxelṣen, ma d nețțat tseddeq ciṭṭuh-nni s wayes ara tɛic.
Ur țsetḥin ur țneḥcamen, xeddmen anagar leɛṛuṛ yerna ur sɛin ara leqniɛa.
Ad ilin tnac lsisan i geččan, ṛṛezq-ed si lɛinseṛ. Mi gcerreg di beṛṛa, wid akk yețțujerden di lexla iwakken ad ilin di tnac yid-sen.
Ma d win ițwamelken, ur ilaq ara a d-yeǧǧ kra n wayen yețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ, ur ilaq ara ad yemḥeq.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet.
Lemmer nezzenz leɛṭeṛ-nni, tili yewwi-d ssuma tameqqrant ara nefṛeq i lɣaci.
Wid yețțaɣen znuzun leḥwayeǧ di temdint-agi yuɣalen d imeṛkantiyen, ad qqimen mebɛid ad aggaden a ten-taweḍ twaɣit, ad ččen ;
ijeḥnaḍ-agi-ines, tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen meṛṛa ɣef lecɣal-is.
Tzemrem aț-țzemrem ɣer lkețțan aṛqaq yețfeǧǧiǧen. Lkețțan-agi i gesṛuḥen deg wemkan-nni anda akken i sen-yebḍa, aț-țɛeqleḍ belli ɣelṭen ɣef wayen yeɛnan tamsalt-is.
Imawlan n Sidna Ɛisa țṛuḥun mkul lǧiha ɣer mkul amkan iwakken aț-țili d yiwet n tmurt.
Wid i gḥeḍren ḥekkun-d i wiyaḍ ayen yedṛan d win yețwazedɣen.
Zzin-as-d leswaṛ n temdint n Lquds, ț-țilawin-nsen s wayes ara tenṛekḍen. Llan azal n tǧehden, azal n meyya amezwaru n tlata iberdan i d-yețwaceggɛen a ten-id-ersen.
Lɛeskeṛ bɣan ad nɣen imeḥbas-nni axaṭer uggaden a sen-rewlen s lɛum.
M'ara d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, bɣan ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen. M'ara ɣeṛqent lqayen rrif n lebḥeṛ, a d-yawi waḍu ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ yuɣal ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ.
Lqebṭan-nni iḍeggeṛ-ed akk armi armi ț-țamdint n Tirt, yeqqim armi ɛawdeḍ-it azal n telt. Ulac win i s-yețṛaǧun alamma d amakar.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiṛṛem ɣef txeṣṣar nni n ddunit meṛṛa, ɣef ddemma n temsalin-agi țxelliṣen deg iberdan n tlata iberdan.
Ula d aqeddac n Sidna Ɛisa ilaq a d-yas lweqt i deg ara yedṛu wayen i d-yekker ɣer yemdanen n ddunit. Ad ițțujeṛṛeb si tmura i d-yekkan si temdint n Birinit, iwakken ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa n umeqqran-nsen.
A d-yas umɛellem-is azal n sebɛa yixef n tmes, a ten-yawi 700 si lǧiha n usammer, ara yefnu waḍu n tegzirt-nni ; wid yellan d iɛdawen ur numin ara s Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a d-ffɣen seg imi-k tbeggneḍ.
Lɛeskeṛ ameqqran n leswaṛ-is ṛeqqmen s yezṛa ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf. Ayen i wasif n Lufrat, i wasif n Tilteṛṛit, armi d ɣuṛ-es azeggaɣ daɣen sin iḥewwaten, iwakken ad ihudd a d-yawi ɣer lḥakem n tmurt n Surya.
meɛna m'ara bdunt feccal n leswaṛ-ikuf armi ț-țilawin, qṛib a d-yaweḍ lweqt ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, imiren aț-țenqes akteṛ n ṛebɛa twiztin n lfeṭṭa,
Ilaq ula d yiwen ad yeṭṭef deg wazal n tlata iberdan, yefka iman-is d ameqqran di ddunit iwakken a d-nbeggen acḥal nebɣa a nɛiwen wiyaḍ. M'ara t-id-yaweḍ ɣuṛ-es, axaṭer ilaq aț-țenɛețțab kra n yemdanen yid-es aț-țenɛețțab.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed tnac n lɣellat, mkul agur tețțak-ed lfakya. Iferrawen-is d ddwa yesseḥlayen lǧețța.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i uceṭṭiḍ aqdim, lameɛna a t-nnernin aț-țejdit ɣef waṭas n lecɣal yelhan i gzemren ad cerken.
ilaq ad yeṭṭef deg awal n Sidi Ṛebbi yellan ț-țideț akken i t-yelmed, iwakken ad yizmir ad isselmed, ad inhu wiyaḍ yerna a d-isbeggen i wiyaḍ ayen i d-yekkaten deg awal-agi, belli ɣelṭen.
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, țxemmimen kan ɣef wayen yedṛan yid-sen, daymi i sen-yețțunefken a sen-tili d lemtel.
