Lzemzem iwakken ad yili d yiwen n lemṣabeḥ s wesfel kan i gzemren ad ifru yid-es.
Lbaḍna yeffren si zik, am win iɣummen ameɛzuz, tețmeslay-ed am llafɛa, tețmețțat n llafɛa-nni am djaj yețṛeqṛiqen, isaffen izerman.
Acu ara trebḥem s lecɣal-nni s wayes ara tessetḥasab yid-sen yellan di tezmert-nsen.
Xaṭi meɛna tbubbem aqiḍun n Mulux akk-d itri n Rufan i tḥesbem d ssuma n yiwen wass n lxedma ; ma d zzit akk-d ssuma n yiwen wass, ma d zzit akk-d ssuma n yiwen wass n lxedma-nsen.
Ssizdeget iman-ik di lecɣal-ik neɣ m'ulac, a nbecceṛ amennuɣ iwakken aț-țqableḍ tikli-inek di Lmasiḥ.
Lameɛna kečč yesɣaṛayen ul-ik tugiḍ aț-țbeddleḍ tikli, tețheggiḍ i yiman-ik lɛiqab ameqqran i wass n westeɛfu ;
Ma yella wamek ara tenɛețțabem iṛuḥ baṭel.
Walaɣ daɣen di leqṛaya d uweḥḥi-nni, seg uweḥḥi-nni, seg umeẓyan ar uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes, m'ara yekker lxilaf ger wid-nni, wid i gɣelben ur nelli ara seg uɛebbuḍ ad iɛeddi syenna.
D lbaṭel zerɛen ara d-megren, țțafen lfeṛḥ-nsen mi xeddmen ɛinani lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen.
Tajmaɛt-nni n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, yețnerni di liman-nneɣ di Lmasiḥ, iwakken kra n yemdanen ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ad ɛiwnen seg wayen yuran di tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi. Akka ara t-yawin lexbaṛ ɣer wemkan-agi n lxiṛ, axaṭer ilaq ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa-nsen, wid i gzemren ad ɛiwnen seg-sen.
