Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla akukru, daymi i geggul d ayen ur nezmir a t-nefhem.
Leṛwaḥ-nni n leǧnun snejmaɛen-d igelliden n ddunit deg yiwen wemkan iwumi qqaṛen s tɛibṛanit « Harmagidun ».
Wid akk yumnen s Lmasiḥ, țɛicin s tdukli yerna beṭṭun wway gar-asen ayen akk sɛan di lɛadda-nsen.
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi azal.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Di teswiɛt-nni tewwet lsizdeget, imeksawen ițnusun di tlemmast n yiḍ.
M'ara yeɣli yiṭij, yebɣa a d-yaweḍ lweqt-nni, iwakken ad ibeddel imensi n Tfaska. Ma ț-țaggara, m'ara d-teḥyu a d-yaweḍ wayen ilaqen, aț-țemfaṛaqem, yal ass i deg ara tseddqem.
Wid akk i gtebɛen tamusni-agi, sṛuḥen liman-nni i sɛan di Lmasiḥ.
Ayen akk i d-yețwaxleq seg uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes, itekkeṛ-ed seg wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit, d ayen ur nezmir a t-nefhem ula d nețța.
Leɛḍima i d-itekken n tudert i gellan d yiwet n lǧețța, mkul ṣṣenf yellan di lewḥuc :
Taxelqit teɣli seddaw leḥkum n leqwanen d uselmed n tideț, iwakken a d-nbeggen belli ț-țideț, lameɛna aṭas n yemdanen i d-yețwaceggɛen s ɣuṛ-es kan i gețmeslay.
Lemfaṣel n lǧețța iwumi ur nefki ara lqima, d nutni i nețḥadar akteṛ n wiyaḍ ; ihi d lemfaṣel ur nezmir ara a d-nebder i nețḥadar aṭas,
Tzemrem aț-țzemrem aț-țeḍlem s lemɣawla ɣer ṣṣifa n wemdan, iwakken aț-țzemrem ayen akk i gețḍuɛun tudert, imi ur txeddmem ara lxilaf ger yemdanen.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) akk-d laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d Baadi.
Ad huddwancin n ttjuṛ, zemmemen aṛqaq ad ṭṭfen imukan imezwura, ad țwajerden s tuɣzi-nsen. Iqleb am umeẓyan, ad țwaɣedṣen s waṭas n tmanyin nniḍen, ad țwaɣedṣen iwakken a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, ad țwajeṛben.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, tețțeddu-d yiwet n tbuciḍant-nni armi d ṛebɛa meyya utlatin n uɛebbuḍ akk-d meyya twiztin n lfeṭṭa.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, tețțunefk-as tezmert a s-fken yal lɣella.
Leɛqed amezwaru yesɛa leqwanen yesɛan daɣen amkan anda ɛebbden Ṛebbi.
Tuɣalem d axxam yebnan ɣef tayeḍ, a d-fkeɣ azal n mitin i cudden si ṛebɛa tɣemmaṛ, iwakken a ten-issiweḍ ccan akk-d igelliden n ddunit.
A nețkel ihi, a nqeṛṛeb ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi anda tella tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi, iwakken a naf ssmaḥ, a ɣ-iɛiwen di lweqt ilaqen.
Ma ț-țideț, aṭas deg wid i ten-ittabaɛen, iwakken ad uɣalen d imezwura s lewkil ɣef yiman-nsen.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i ttejṛa nniḍen i gzemren a t-iqleɛ. Llan aṭas n yemdanen daɣen i gzemren a t-iwalin akk-d kra n wayen yedṛan. Kra deg-sen i gezmer ad amnen belli tudert-agi, tudert n dayem di ddunit nniḍen.
Neɣ daɣen m'ur neɛqil ara mliḥ akteṛ n temẓin, acḥal ihi tedṛa d abrid i gzemren ad iqdec ɣef Sidi Ṛebbi.
A wen-d-iniɣ yiwet n wussan : deg ussan-nni a d-isbeggen ṛṛeḥma-s tameqqrant i lejdud-nwen ; nutni ara yilin ț-țaɛkumt ɣef yimawen-nsen.
Aṭas n lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen n mkul ṣṣifa, axaṭer llan wid itețțen ayla n wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ, ma d aṭas n wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ.
Lebḥuṛ i nesɛedday tura xfif yerna ur țfeṛṛi ara, yal yiwen seg-sen ur ț-țizmir ara ad yili win iɣummen aman yelhan, axaṭer d lexṛif i waḍu, ur țțaǧan ara daɣen a d-beggnen iman-nsen zdat Sidi Ṛebbi.
Lxuluq-nni, mkul m'ara yeɣli yiṭij ɣef ddunit ; lebḥur, ɣeṛqen-iten ad meggren, m'ara slen yis.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet.
