M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam, awi-inek ț-țamusni, aɛessas, a ț-iḍeggeṛ ɣer lqaɛa, a ɣ-iɛiwen di leɛmeṛ, aț-țesbeddeḍ di taɛessas, zdat-es uqbel a tent-yebɛem ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ini-yasen daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ad beccṛen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, wiyaḍ d imeksawen n tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen neɣ d wid yesselmaden agdud n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ayen akken i t-id-ideṛṛun di mkul amkan akk-d țid i d-iteddun, ur nezmir ara a d-sbeggnen belli ccetwa fell-asen belli d ayen i gkeččmen iman-nsen.
Akken imdanen ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ a d-cehden fell-as s lxiṛ ur țțafen ara deg-s wayen ara s-d ssukksen, bɣan ad rren iman-nsen ɣer yiman-nsen.
?adret ɣef yiman-ik aț-țiḥsiḍ ɣef Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen, a k-rnuḍ s tukciwin i d-iteffɣen seg wezṛu iteddun s mkul ṣṣenf. D annect-agi i gețțawin ɣer nnger, daymi imdanen meṛṛa ad xedmen ccɣel-ik.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen yelhan, ur ilaq ara ad yili d sebba n diri.
lɣaci wwḍen armi srusun ɣef yimuḍan ula ț-țimucwaṛin neɣ iceṭṭiḍen yennulen Bulus, dɣa imuḍan ḥellun, wid akk yețțumelken țeffɣen ten leǧnun.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem, aț-țedṛu di tmurt n Jlili.
Ekkset si gar-awen uqbel a d-yedṛu wayen i wen-yewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi, iwakken a d-isbeggen belli ɣelṭen deg wexxam-agi, d lewkil ɣef wayla-nni, axaṭer win ixuṣṣen di lefhama-nsen akken ilaq.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n wid iɣummen. Lexṣaf-nni, tekcem-iten lxelɛa ț-țewwa i genneɛtaben di tmurt-nsen.
Tusa-d yiwet n taǧǧalt tigellilt tessers sin iṣurdiyen yesɛan azal n ṛebɛa twiztin n lfeṭṭa.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ? Neɣ m'ara qeṛṛben ɣer imukan iḍeṛfen neɣ ț-țimezduɣin n waman.
Ur nețțuɣal a nsel i tejmaɛt n wid yekkaten snitra d wid i gcennun akk-d wid yekkaten ajewwaq d lbuq. Kra n wakal, ur d-tewqiɛ ara lmeɛna deg yiman-is kan iwakken a ten-tekkes akren s lexṣaṣ, neɣ a tent-id-kksen ɣef kra n wayen yuran di tira iqedsen.
Ad ilḥu s lebɛid, a d-ḍefṛen tamurt n laṣel, ad yawi yid-es ṭṭmeɛ n tmurt n laṣel-is.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Akka i glaq aț-țețmeslayeḍ, aț-țnehhuḍ, aț-țețheggiḍ s lemɣawla.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ. Lameɛna ass-a mazal-iț ar ass-a ilaq ad yili d dderya i gzemren ad țțaɣen awal.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Lquds, llan wid yettabaɛen annect-agi azal n meyya iberdan.
Tajmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, ț-țigzirt n Lufrat. Deg ukețțan azeggaɣ daɣen ɛecṛa temdinin-nni, wwin-t yeddurin yid-es meyya twiztin n lfeṭṭa,
Bulus d Silas ɛeddan si temdinin n Anfizunya akk-d Rassen, ufan-d atmaten yellan di tegzirt n Basalun iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi. Mi gella di tmurt n Barsulya akk-d Rassen, usan-d ɣer wexxam n Biri.
Aṭas n lewṣayat i glaq aț-țxelṣeḍ uqbel ad kemmlen abrid-agi, meɛna m'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt ɣer wemkan-nni.
ṭṭmeɛ, ssexṛeb, lɛaddat-agi si mkul ṣṣenf, ur nețbeddil ara, ur ikeččem ara wayen yelhan d wayen akk yellan di ddunit, ur xeddmet ara lxilaf ger yemdanen, m'ara yili gar-awen d sebba n tuccḍa, ur ilaq ara a d-yedṛu ayen ara yedṛun ɣer wemkan agi.
Ilaq-aɣ a neṛǧun mkul lweqt, iwakken ur țțafen ara ayen n diri ara hedṛen fell-aneɣ neɣ ad nneḥcamen.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Leɛqed ciṭṭuḥ n temdint ɣer tayeḍ, a d-yaf zeddigen, wid ixeddmen cceṛ, wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tuǧǧal meẓẓiyen di leɛmeṛ, ma yella rriɣ aṭas n yedrimen-nni ixeddmen asekkak n yirden d ssuma tameqqrant, ama deg ufellaḥ-nni ama di lxedma-nsen, ixeddmen ayen i wen-d-wwiɣ.
Ma d kečč m'ara tseddqeḍ, ilaq afus-ik ayeffus ur ițwali ara wayen ixeddem lbeṛhanat imeqqranen,
Exdem lmeǧhud-ik iwakken a d taseḍ uqbel ccetwa deg-sent ama di temda n waman ama di lebḥuṛ.
Ma yella tebɣiḍ aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq neɣ wid n zzhu n ddunit ? Neɣ m'ulac wid yebɣan a d-yefk ayen i gɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi, neɣ m'ulac ilaq-iyi ad xedmen annect-agi, am akken i t-yelhuɣ.
Yerna mazal-ikkun tețzuxxum ! Ilaq-awen aț-țiliḍ di leɛtab, argaz i gxeddmen annect-agi ilaq a t tessufɣem si tejmaɛt ;
Wid yețțaɣen znuzun leḥwayeǧ di temdint-agi yuɣalen d lemtel, iwakken ad ilin di tzzin rennun, ad fken iseflawen ɣef telwiḥt-nsen d ssuma n yiwen wass wis xemsin.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem, neɣ m'ulac ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ;
Imeslayen-agi « tikkelt nniḍen daɣen » sbeggnen-d belli ayen yețwaxelqen ad yenhezz ad yenger iwakken a d-yeqqim kan wayen yețdumun.
M'ara tețwaqehṛem deg yiwet n tegniț i wen-d-ițțunefken, a d-tban acḥal yelha m'ara kemmlet tikli, teṭṭfem di liman-nwen.
Tejreḥ tasa-w iwakken ad zegren yiwet n tɣuṛfeț, a k-yessiweḍ lexbaṛ, tețfeǧǧiǧ, alamma qṛib a d-yeqqim lateṛ-ik.
Ițțuceggɛeɣ-d ad beccṛeɣ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ; ɣef ddemma-s i lliɣ d ameḥbus ; dɛut ihi ɣer wat leǧnas nniḍen ur nelli ara seg wat Isṛail.
Axaṭer ilaq a d-yedṛu wayen ara sen-d-yawi Bulus ɣer webrid, yerna ad isseɛṛeq imeḥbas-nni iwakken ad iheggi iman-is.
Deg ussan-nni aṭas n tudrin i gxeddmen ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, daymi i ț-țaɛerḍen wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen. Qqimet di tețqellibem a wen-nesteqsi.
Deg ussan-nni, yiwen ur izmir a d-yas lweqt i deg ara t-yeṭṭef wemkan-nni alamma ț-țaggara, meɛna m'ara s-heggin iman-is ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, nekk s yiman-iw a t-t-id-iniɣ.
Asirem-nni yebnan ɣef lsas, ur t-tečči ara tmes wayen akken yebna, a t-txedmem ula d yiwen uqiḍun n temlilit yella di lebḥin-nni s ufella n uweḥḥi.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna ț-țezmert i wid i d-ițeffɣen seg wezṛu iteddun i webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ițeddun ț-țaɛkumt, daɣen wid i d-ițeffɣen seg waṭas n lɛaddat n yemdanen, llant-aɣ-d daɣen wid yețxalafen iman-nsen.
Llan ihi alamma rriɣ aṭas n tudrin di mkul amkan n tmurt n Bubulun i d-ițeddun ț-țmurt n yiḍ, ur țțafen ara ayen ara yernun di mkul amkan iwakken a ț-țkecmeḍ deg-s mbla ma nɛedda ɣer temdint n Ludikus.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus neɣ deg unyir-nsen,
Atah wayen ara tweṣṣiḍ tuǧǧal iwakken ur d-yețțili ara wayen ara sent-d-ssukksen ɣer tmurt-agi. Ɣef ddemma n lweqt i deg ara yedṛu wannect-agi.
Wiyaḍ țemcabin ɣer wakal yeččuṛen d tegzirt n m'ara d-yas si tmurt n Missik, ț-țigzirt tameqqrant m'ara slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, meɛna qebblen-t-id iwakken a d-isbeggen s waṭas n yemdanen.
Ur sṭuqqutet ara awal mbla lmeɛna ɣef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud neɣ čaqlalat d umenɣi.
Meɛna ɣas akken walan aṭas n yemdanen i gellan, ur qebblen ara ad ḥekmen fell-asen s lmut, ț-țimeslayt n wid i d-ițeffɣen seg-s axaṭer d lexṣaṣuṛ ɣef waṭas n iqermuden.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Llan deg-s lkețțan azeggaɣ ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb, wiyaḍ ad țwaxedmen s wezṛu am usigna, m'ara yexdem lbeṛhanat ur nesɛi lmeɛna, aț-țwehmem iman-nsen.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n Sidna Ɛisa.
Ma tebɣiḍ ihi aț-țkemleḍ deg webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi qleɛ iman-ik tḍeggṛeḍ ɣer ifassen-ik wala a tkecmeḍ ɣer zdat-ek iwakken a k-iḥaseb.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Ur ilaq ara ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa-nsen, m'ur ten-id-yerr ara waḍu ɣer zdat.
Deg umkan-agi iqedsen yella yiwen n leḥjab ifeṛqen amkan iqedsen d umkan iqedsen nezzeh,
