Uggadeɣ mbla ma nɛedda i tlisa n ccɣel-iw wala ad yaɣ awal-iw.
Deg ifragen-agi aṭas n imuḍan i gḍelqen, iderɣalen, iɛibanen d wukrifen țṛaǧun akk ad ḥerrken waman. ?čuṛen akk-d kra n ccnawi i d-yegran.
D nețța i geqqimen yid-es sin yergazen n tegzirt-nni. Mi ɛeddan si temdint n Tiberyas, zzuɣṛen-d si temdint n Tiberyas, n Miri-nni isem-is Zalufas akk-d Tawṛat, wis tlata iwumi qqaṛen daɣen : « Wagi tadist ».
