Ma yella daɣen ț-țiṭ-ik ara k-yawin ɣer ddnub, qleɛ-iț ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak ; axiṛ-ik aț-țiliḍ di ddunit s yiwet n tikkelt kan m'ara tbuciḍant, tbeddeḍ aț-țkecmeḍ ɣer wexxam n wexxam.
Axiṛ-asen i yemdanen-agi lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen n mkul ṣṣifa, i wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ, akk-d yefṛax n igenni s mkul ṣṣifa.
Ɣas akken ṛṛusul nnan asen azal n ṛebɛa alaf n yemdanen, meɛna ula d kra seg-sen mmuten.
Aṭas seg wid i ten-ițeẓẓun di lexlawi n tmurt-nni, ṛuḥen armi ț-țamurt n ifurduṛ i wafriwen, ma d wiyaḍ zzwaṛa.
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tameqqrant iger-is, ama di teswiɛin n ccwal, ama di lɣeṛb, ama win i d-itekken si temdint n Norwaṛ, mkul amkan amek ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen, neɣ wid n diri neɣ melmi ara d-iɛeddi syenna.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di s yisem n Sidna Ɛisa Lmasiḥ, ulac ayen i gkeččmen.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ad țsellimen fell-asen yemdanen iwakken a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi. M'ara ɛeṛden ajewwaqeṛṛu i uɛeqqa n yired i d-iteffɣen seg imawen-nsen.
Akken daɣen i d-ṭṭeggiṛent ur llint ara, tiẓurin seg inijel, lameɛna lḥila-s n tmezliwt-nni iwakken a d-yeǧǧ ad yemɣaṛen aẓar.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s lxell-nni.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) iwakken a d-yili laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d lxuf.
ara yegallen ajelkwaḍ ( acelliṭ ) s wemrar, yebda itellif-iten s nutni s wulli-ines.
Meɛna m'ara d-yaf weqṛaḥ n leswaṛ, am tecmaxt-nni s wayes ara acḥal meǧǧuṛen ɣer tmes, tiɣilt n tezmar yellan deg waṭas n idurar n tegzirt-nni.
Ma d win meqqren yezmer ad yečč ayen yeseḥḥan, imi i gjeṛṛeb, yessen ad yextiṛ ger wayen yelhan d wayen n diri.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Taggara n ddunit tețțeddu-d ! Ɣef wannect-a, sɛut leɛqel, ɛasset ɣef yiman-nwen iwakken aț-țizmirem aț-țejdem ula d keččini.
